{"word":"G937 - βασιλικός - basilikós - bas-il-ee-kos' - King's","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βασιλικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">basilikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bas-il-ee-kos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">King's</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ராஜா, ராஜரிக - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of or belonging to a king, kingly, royal, regal"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G935 - βασιλεύς - basileús - bas-il-yooce'/935\">G935</a>; <i>regal</i> (in relation), that is, (literally) belonging to (or befitting) the sovereign (as land, dress, or a <i>courtier</i>), or (figuratively) <i>preeminent:</i> - king&rsquo;s, nobleman, royal.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G932/932\">G932</a>, <a href=\"#/G934/934\">G934</a>, <a href=\"#/G935/935\">G935</a>, <a href=\"#/G936/936\">G936</a>, <a href=\"#/G937/937\">G937</a>, <a href=\"#/G938/938\">G938</a>"}]}